{"tid":1793293,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"偽黃店真係防不勝防","createTime":"2019-12-22T09:50:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T13:58:29.000Z","uid":94127,"like":22,"dislike":141,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"ded92db181f2e1fc0f9b89060cb28eb31909339e","tid":1793293,"uid":94127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T09:50:36.000Z","msg":"呢間店最開始都見佢都幾有心機搞，但係抗爭<br />\n<br />\n開始後 我諗呢間店開始藉機扮黃吸客，開始<br />\n<br />\n見佢生意轉好。但係有日比我聽到話老細將客<br />\n<br />\n買單唔洗找啲錢自己袋左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(個客話將啲錢買<br />\n<br />\n水比手足)<br />\n<br />\n運動開始後就只見呢間野係咁加價，就冇其他<br />\n<br />\n作為，啲野又難食。希望大家注意食用<br />\n<br />\n位於筲箕灣 大x家 x丼家 大丼x<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XmU8R9T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXmU8R9T.jpg&h=d05d81d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5uzpquS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5uzpquS.jpg&h=9559f6e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d24bae9278ae8d92f795da4b11aab16607fa8eb9","tid":1793293,"uid":94127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T09:51:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8783afc6eedbc6106aec044cbbe45878cf202c65","tid":1793293,"uid":94127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T09:51:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c0660ccaeceee42493e1530fe21653545f2d381","tid":1793293,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T09:51:47.000Z","msg":"【核彈】呢個方法可以防水炮車【行動po求推】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778898</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【行動po】【求推】點解1223去稅局 連登冇人講？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1792093\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1792093</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n點解1223稅局冇人提？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1781990\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1781990</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n