睇佢唔係食人血饅頭<br />\n但佢連澄清都唔肯 咁都無野好講"},{"pid":"bb9cf3dbe014e637d8e047922cfca78e553bc672","tid":1793293,"uid":65556,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c45bf5deea15bdb61db3bfca540614e89026dac2","tid":1793293,"uid":94127,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T09:54:50.000Z","msg":"自己親耳聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T09:59:44.000Z","msg":"其實真係好多仆街借勢呃錢"},{"pid":"9960f97127d9225f5d78ab39ae0b7da07c7432b3","tid":1793293,"uid":329698,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"6b05c545fa21a8b678e4e4c74dde02cbb6bcae05","tid":1793293,"uid":265192,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T09:54:24.000Z","msg":"美心割席轉色都照幫襯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T10:01:13.000Z","msg":"割席接受<br />\n但係都幫襯唔落<br />\n難食到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca6b71ed1b16910d7148556b9570f417a19cd92c","tid":1793293,"uid":118125,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T10:11:06.000Z","msg":"任何傳聞都係聽下就算, 唔駛咁認真<br />\n人血饅頭既店舖食一兩次就知道咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似MK有間店張單據打D字「香港人加油」<br />\n但D野又貴又難食, 出面有防暴就準備落閘趕人走<br />\n所以我幫親主要都係活動初期既深黃店, <br />\n唔好見到「香港人加油」就當佢黃, 尤其呢個口號可以食兩邊茶禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ad580a91f0c7a4808849cb78c6ce9441ff7d59","tid":1793293,"uid":228143,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T10:14:11.000Z","msg":"不嬲多扮黃  <br />\n<br />\n我只信蕭生<br />\n<br />\n去人民超市 <br />\n<br />\n去時代堅石燒 <br />\n<br />\nfc左穩陣"},{"pid":"a9ee8a929313e5eb3455315a195cfd9ce098f9fb","tid":1793293,"uid":28435,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T10:15:37.000Z","msg":"門檻宜低不宜高，要偽黃壯大個經濟圈"},{"pid":"2505c54ad864e22b78144748b3d1ba7c8895714b","tid":1793293,"uid":59989,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T10:15:38.000Z","msg":"其實對住呢啲偽黃店幫佢地煲大佢係最好<br />\n根本唔需要同講佢扮黃<br />\n煲到藍絲都知<br />\n咪逼到佢一定要歸黃色"},{"pid":"5aec463db40a051a164988ec23b275a09b296336","tid":1793293,"uid":33614,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T10:18:45.000Z","msg":"認真咁講 你要捐錢自己捐啦<br />\n<br />\n黃店就要無啦啦幫你手捐咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f55f8a04a96f4a844381fbadeb039be6f292bcd","tid":1793293,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T10:27:32.000Z","msg":"大家星期日有時間，記住加入香港金融業職工總會做會員呀！<br />\n<br />\n我哋可唔可以為大家發聲，可以做到咩地步，全靠會員的支持<br />\n<br />\n冇會員，政府點解要理你呢，資方點解要理你呢...<br />\n<br />\n所以唔好等，今日就加入啦<br />\n<br />\nPS: 就算唔係金融界的同業，都麻煩like and share，俾多一個人睇到，就多一分機會團結同路人，拜托拜托🙏<br />\n<br />\n#香港金融業職工總會<br />\n#香港金總<br />\n#HKFU<br />\n#收會員<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/107457800635080/posts/159723118741881/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F107457800635080%2Fposts%2F159723118741881%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=QEbR3JiquQCbCEiBABctD6nyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=1d668409\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/107457800635080/posts/159723118741881/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"b6496bd61231e1f1bc53cc6ea19726dadc732fd9","tid":1793293,"uid":71195,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"c57158362c1b6cb41edf7aeeebabae4e8668ccd4","tid":1793293,"uid":265192,"like":102,"dislike":5,"score":97,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T09:53:43.000Z","msg":"唔需要捉鬼，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鼓勵轉色、包容偽黃</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T10:37:14.000Z","msg":"啱 我地係需要更多同路人 而唔係拒之門外"},{"pid":"ca558030f1333a00e128b5f554ba2a5bdd73cf61","tid":1793293,"uid":91511,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T10:42:18.000Z","msg":"得一兩句就話係偽黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我食過呢間幾次，張單上面會有口號，最記得係佢喺區選之後印左句新口號上去，我就覺得佢地貼得幾