, 出面有防暴就準備落閘趕人走<br />\n所以我幫親主要都係活動初期既深黃店, <br />\n唔好見到「香港人加油」就當佢黃, 尤其呢個口號可以食兩邊茶禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T11:22:59.000Z","msg":"其實黃店都唔應該捉鬼<br />\n因為你永遠唔知邊間偽黃定真黃<br />\n<br />\n再捉就成個黃色經濟圈會散，扮黃都有佢的作用<br />\n起馬可以孤立班藍"},{"pid":"3103c52aee21367b643e7341055682b46312437e","tid":1793293,"uid":293896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T11:23:54.000Z","msg":"鼓勵轉色 照幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你捉偽黃 捉一世都捉唔曬"},{"pid":"6889669b9c06735f7cc911f3e43d856c4aa24ed5","tid":1793293,"uid":159428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T11:23:59.000Z","msg":"好煩 偽撚完未<br />\n仲有 黃都好 唔需要專登去消費<br />\n重點係: 有必須要嘅使費就去黃店"},{"pid":"2194ff5c649f9e96501556be580768600b3a413c","tid":1793293,"uid":31723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T11:30:29.000Z","msg":"哩啲問題同捉鬼一樣<br />\n又浪費時間 又對吸納同伴冇幫助<br />\n特別係團體成立初期 你set個道德門檻咁高啲人點加入<br />\n<br />\n希望樓主唔係假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2479643f924c315ad9385642fc887d9101a8181","tid":1793293,"uid":11895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T11:30:41.000Z","msg":"證據？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef7d4932c1c02af5604612675de06f5fab4a44b6","tid":1793293,"uid":163024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T11:31:27.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n利申 依家食緊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EPzHXdq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEPzHXdq.png&h=8df3040e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1bcdfdb439cb2abd8e374a0243e0c3b47dd8f5a8","tid":1793293,"uid":6103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T11:47:03.000Z","msg":"d死仆街好驚黃色經濟圈成功<br />\n借d椅去中傷一d唔起眼小型黃店or 唔敢表態ge店舖<br />\n，從而帶風向煽動我地制裁錯d 小店<br />\n<br />\n我地真係要小心，唔好俾呢d仆街呃到"},{"pid":"c5fd2e8a2b60665